  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotatedOpModeClassFilter
    Does the heavy lifting of managing annotation-based opmode registrations.
    ClassManager

    OnBotJavaClassLoader

    OpModeManagerImpl is the owner of the concept of a 'current' opmode.

    OpModeManagerImpl.DefaultOpMode is the opmode that the system runs when no user opmode is active.
    OpModeMeta
    OpModeMeta provides information about an OpMode.
    OpModeMetaAndClass
    OpModeMetaAndClass ties together an OpMode class with metadata concerning same.
    OpModeMetaAndInstance
    OpModeMetaAndInstance ties together an OpMode instance with metadata concerning same.
    RegisteredOpModes
    RegisteredOpModes is the owner of a set of currently-registered OpModes.
